View a report's schedule on the Schedule Report page or from the Reports tab. To create, edit, and delete reports: Enhanced Folder Sharing permission is required. Available in Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

To see the schedule for a report on the Reports tab, hover over  in the  column. Users need the Schedule Reports permission to see the icon and information.

Only users with the “View Setup and Configuration” permission can view scheduled reports for your organization from Setup, enter Scheduled Jobs in the Quick Find box, then select Scheduled Jobs.
